<inglise>Chapter 8 </inglise>
<eesti>L&otilde;pps&auml;tted </eesti>
<inglise>Final Provisions </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 32. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 32. </inglise>
<eesti>Vaidluste lahendamine </eesti>
<inglise>Dispute resolution </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Peretoetuste m&auml;&auml;ramise otsusega mitten&otilde;ustumise korral on toetuse taotlejal &otilde;igus p&ouml;&ouml;rduda pensionikomisjoni poole 30 p&auml;eva jooksul, arvates otsuse saamise p&auml;evast. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) Upon disagreement with a decision on grant of family benefits, an applicant for benefits has the right of recourse to a pension committee within thirty days after the date of receipt of the decision. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Pensionikomisjoni otsusega mitten&otilde;ustumise korral on toetuse taotlejal &otilde;igus p&ouml;&ouml;rduda halduskohtusse 30 p&auml;eva jooksul, arvates vaideotsuse isikule teatavaks tegemise p&auml;evast. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) Upon disagreement with a decision of a pension committee, an applicant for benefits has the right of recourse to an administrative court within thirty days as of the date on which the person is notified of the decision. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 33. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 33. </inglise>
<eesti>Varem m&auml;&auml;ratud peretoetuste s&auml;ilitamine </eesti>
<inglise>Continued payment of family benefits granted earlier </inglise>
<eesti>Isikule, kellele peretoetused on m&auml;&auml;ratud enne 2002. aasta 1. jaanuari, kuid keda ei loeta k&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect; 2 alusel peretoetustele &otilde;igust omavaks isikuks, makstakse peretoetusi, kui ta vastab muudele k&auml;esolevas seaduses s&auml;testatud tingimustele. </eesti>
<inglise>Family benefits shall be paid to persons to whom family benefits have been granted before 1 January 2002, but who are not deemed to be persons with the right to receive family benefits pursuant to &sect; 2 of this Act, if they fulfil other conditions provided for in this Act. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 34. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 34. </inglise>
<eesti>&Otilde;igusaktide muutmine </eesti>
<inglise>Amendment of legislation </inglise>
<eesti>Sotsiaalmaksuseaduse (RT I 2000, 102, 675; 2001, 50, 285; 59, 359; 79, 480; 91, 544) &sect; 6 l&otilde;ike 1 punkt 1 muudetakse ja s&otilde;nastatakse j&auml;rgmiselt: </eesti>
<inglise>Clause 6 (1) 1) of the Social Tax Act (RT I 2000, 102, 675; 2001, 50, 285; 59, 359; 79, 480; 91, 544) is amended and worded as follows: </inglise>
<eesti>"1) isik, kellele makstakse lapsehooldustasu riiklike peretoetuste seaduse (RT I 2001, 95, 587) &sect; 6 l&otilde;ike 1 punkti 1, l&otilde;ike 5 v&otilde;i 6 alusel, ja mittet&ouml;&ouml;tav vanem, kellele makstakse lapsehooldustasu nimetatud seaduse &sect; 6 l&otilde;ike 1 punkti 3 ja l&otilde;ike 3 alusel;". </eesti>
<inglise>"1) persons who are paid child care allowance pursuant to clause 6 (1) 1) or subsections 6 (5) or (6) of the State Family Benefits Act (RT I 2001, 95, 587), and non-working parents who are paid child care allowance pursuant to clause 6 (1) 3) and subsection 6 (3) of the specified Act;". </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 35. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 35. </inglise>
<eesti>&Otilde;igusaktide kehtetuks tunnistamine </eesti>
<inglise>Repeal of legislation </inglise>
<eesti>K&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumisel tunnistatakse kehtetuks riiklike peretoetuste seadus (RT I 1997, 42, 676; 77, 1309; 1998, 86/87, 1407; 1999, 10, 150; 16, 273; 67, 657; 82, 749; 2000, 102, 668). </eesti>
<inglise>The State Family Benefits Act (RT I 1997, 42, 676; 77, 1309; 1998, 86/87, 1407; 1999, 10, 150; 16, 273; 67, 657; 82, 749; 2000, 102, 668) is repealed upon the entry into force of this Act. </inglise>
